      "title": "CT AORTIC ANGIOGRAM at Cadabams Diagnostics – Fast, Safe & Accurate ",
      "description": "CT Aortic Angiogram at Cadabams: Painless, high-resolution vascular imaging. Expert care, same-day reports. Trusted for 1000+ monthly scans.",
